verses.text: O \w clap|strong="H8628"\w* your \w hands|strong="H3709"\w*, all ye \w people|strong="H5971"\w*; \w shout|strong="H7321"\w* unto \w God|strong="H0430"\w* with the \w voice|strong="H6963"\w* of \w triumph|strong="H7440"\w*.\f + \fr 47.1 \ft for: or, of\f*

For the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* most \w high|strong="H5945"\w* \add is\add* \w terrible|strong="H3372"\w*; \add he is\add* a \w great|strong="H1419"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* over all the \w earth|strong="H0776"\w*.
He shall \w subdue|strong="H1696"\w* the \w people|strong="H5971"\w* under us, and the \w nations|strong="H3816"\w* under our \w feet|strong="H7272"\w*.

He shall \w choose|strong="H0977"\w* our \w inheritance|strong="H5159"\w* for us, the \w excellency|strong="H1347"\w* of \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* whom he \w loved|strong="H0157"\w*. \w Selah|strong="H5542"\w*.

\w God|strong="H0430"\w* is gone \w up|strong="H5927"\w* with a \w shout|strong="H8643"\w*, the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* with the \w sound|strong="H6963"\w* of a \w trumpet|strong="H7782"\w*.

Sing \w praises|strong="H2167"\w* to \w God|strong="H0430"\w*, sing \w praises|strong="H2167"\w*: sing \w praises|strong="H2167"\w* unto our \w King|strong="H4428"\w*, sing \w praises|strong="H2167"\w*.

For \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \add is\add* the \w King|strong="H4428"\w* of all the \w earth|strong="H0776"\w*: sing ye \w praises|strong="H2167"\w* with \w understanding|strong="H7919"\w*.\f + \fr 47.7 \ft with: or, every one that hath\f*

\w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w reigneth|strong="H4427"\w* over the \w heathen|strong="H1471"\w*: \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w sitteth|strong="H3427"\w* upon the \w throne|strong="H3678"\w* of his \w holiness|strong="H6944"\w*.

The \w princes|strong="H5081"\w* of the \w people|strong="H5971"\w* are gathered \w together|strong="H0622"\w*, \add even\add* the \w people|strong="H5971"\w* of the \w God|strong="H0430"\w* of \w Abraham|strong="H0085"\w*: for the \w shields|strong="H4043"\w* of the \w earth|strong="H0776"\w* \add belong\add* unto \w God|strong="H0430"\w*: he is \w greatly|strong="H3966"\w* \w exalted|strong="H5927"\w*.\f + \fr 47.9 \ft princesâ€¦: or, voluntary of the people are gathered unto the people of the God of Abraham\f*
